  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 320°F (160°C).",
    "Place shredded mozzarella in a mixing bowl.",
    "Add room temperature butter and lemon juice, mixing well until cheese is fully coated with the mixture.",
    "Season with salt. Mix gently but thoroughly to prevent breaking up of cheese.",
    "Transfer mixture evenly into a greased baking dish or shallow ramekin.",
    "Bake for 10-15 minutes or until edges are golden brown and topping is bubbly."
